requestBody.description:
A list of telemetry measurements made by the device.

Timestamp cannot be more than 10 minutes in the future.

Example of telemetry with GSM measurements
---

```
[{
    "scan": {
        "gsm": [{
            "mcc": 262,
            "mnc": 1,
            "lac": 5126,
            "cid": 16504,
            "nmr": [
                 { "bsic": "6", "bcch": "82" },
                 { "bsic": "7", "bcch": "85" },
                 { "bsic": "12", "bcch": "93" },
                 { "bsic": "13", "bcch": "88" },
                 { "bsic": "19", "bcch": "88" }
            ]
        }]
    },
    "payload": {
        "sensor": "data"
    },
    "timestamp": 1515169948976
}]
```

